{"kind": "daily", "date": "2026-07-10", "html": "<div style=\"font-family:-apple-system,'PingFang TC','Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;color:#16213e;\">\n<div style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#1a2b4a;border-left:5px solid #5b8def;padding-left:12px;margin:0 0 18px;\">📰 每日 AI 新聞 Top 10 · 2026-07-10</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eef4ff;border-left:5px solid #5b8def;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#5b8def;font-weight:800;\">1.</span> Fidji Simo Steps Down From Leading OpenAI's AGI Work Due to Illness<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#3b6cf6;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Fidji Simo 因病卸任 OpenAI AGI 部門負責人</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">OpenAI's Fidji Simo is departing her full-time role as the company's AGI chief and transitioning to a part-time advisor role, following a medical leave for a neuroimmune condition.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">OpenAI 的 Fidji Simo 將卸下 AGI 部門全職主管職位，轉任兼職顧問，此前她因神經免疫疾病請了醫療假。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">The Verge</b> · <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/ai-artificial-intelligence/963738/openai-fidji-simo-steps-down-ceo-advisor\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#ecf7ef;border-left:5px solid #4caf72;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#4caf72;font-weight:800;\">2.</span> OpenAI Launches Its New Family of Models With GPT-5.6<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#1e9e57;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">模型</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">OpenAI 推出 GPT-5.6 新一代模型家族</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">OpenAI's latest model family promises improvements across a range of areas, including cybersecurity capabilities.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">OpenAI 最新模型家族在多項領域帶來提升，包括資安能力的強化。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/09/openai-launches-its-new-family-of-models-with-gpt-5-6/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f1ecfb;border-left:5px solid #8a6bd8;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#8a6bd8;font-weight:800;\">3.</span> OpenAI Is Shutting Down Atlas, but Its AI Browser Ambitions Are Still Growing<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#6b3bf6;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">OpenAI 關閉 Atlas 瀏覽器，但 AI 瀏覽器野心仍在擴張</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">OpenAI is sunsetting its AI-powered browser after less than a year, moving some agentic browsing features to its desktop app and a Chrome extension.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">OpenAI 將在推出不到一年後終止其 AI 瀏覽器 Atlas，並將部分代理式瀏覽功能移植到桌面應用程式與 Chrome 擴充功能。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/09/openai-is-shutting-down-atlas-but-its-ai-browser-ambitions-are-still-growing/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f6f5;border-left:5px solid #2bb0a6;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#2bb0a6;font-weight:800;\">4.</span> Anthropic Found a Hidden Space Where Claude Puzzles Over Concepts<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#0f9b9b;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">研究</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Anthropic 發現 Claude 內部一處「思考概念」的隱藏空間</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Anthropic has developed a technique offering the clearest glimpse yet into what's happening inside large language models as they answer questions or carry out tasks.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Anthropic 研發出一項新技術，讓外界首次得以清楚窺見大型語言模型在回答問題或執行任務時內部的運作情形。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">MIT Technology Review</b> · <a href=\"https://www.technologyreview.com/2026/07/09/1140293/anthropic-found-a-hidden-space-where-claude-puzzles-over-concepts/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fbf3e3;border-left:5px solid #d99b3f;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#d99b3f;font-weight:800;\">5.</span> New York Times Says OpenAI Hid Evidence in ChatGPT Copyright Trial<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b9791f;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">政策</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">紐約時報指控 OpenAI 在 ChatGPT 著作權訴訟中隱匿證據</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">News publishers say OpenAI hid tools and datasets that could identify copyrighted journalism in ChatGPT outputs, escalating their lawsuit with a new motion for sanctions.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">新聞出版商指控 OpenAI 隱藏能辨識 ChatGPT 輸出內容中受著作權保護新聞的工具與資料集，並提出制裁動議升級訴訟。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/09/new-york-times-says-openai-hid-evidence-in-chatgpt-copyright-trial/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fdeef0;border-left:5px solid #e0738a;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#e0738a;font-weight:800;\">6.</span> China Labels Claude Code's Anti-Distillation Mechanism a Security Backdoor<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#d83a5e;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">中國政府將 Claude Code 反蒸餾機制定性為安全後門</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">China's cybersecurity threat database issued a warning claiming Anthropic's Claude Code contains a hidden monitoring mechanism sending sensitive data to remote servers without user consent, urging units to uninstall or upgrade affected versions.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">中國網路安全威脅和漏洞信息共享平臺發布風險提示，指稱 Claude Code 存在未經同意即傳送敏感資訊的監控機制，要求相關單位全面排查並升級或卸載受影響版本。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177212\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f4fb;border-left:5px solid #3f97c9;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#3f97c9;font-weight:800;\">7.</span> Patch for Windows Defender 0-Day Could Allow Attackers to Fill Hard Disk<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#2b7fb0;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Windows Defender 零時差漏洞修補程式恐遭攻擊者濫用塞爆硬碟</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">The ongoing feud between a researcher known as NightmareEclipse and Microsoft over the vulnerability shows no signs of resolving soon.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">研究人員 NightmareEclipse 與微軟之間圍繞該漏洞的爭議仍持續延燒，短期內看不出解決跡象。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">Ars Technica</b> · <a href=\"https://arstechnica.com/security/2026/07/patch-for-windows-defender-0-day-could-allow-attackers-to-fill-hard-disk/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f2f6e8;border-left:5px solid #88a83f;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#88a83f;font-weight:800;\">8.</span> Meta Enters the Crowded AI Coding Battle With Muse Spark 1.1<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#6e8c28;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Meta 推出 Muse Spark 1.1 加入 AI 程式編碼競賽</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Meta pitches Spark's ability to handle large agentic workloads, fix bugs, and assist with large code migrations to enterprises increasingly turning to AI for automation.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Meta 強調 Spark 能處理大型代理式工作負載、修復程式錯誤並協助大型程式碼遷移，瞄準日益仰賴 AI 自動化的企業客戶。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/09/meta-enters-the-crowded-ai-coding-battle-with-muse-spark-1-1/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f9edf6;border-left:5px solid #c56bb0;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#c56bb0;font-weight:800;\">9.</span> Anthropic Wants You to Pay Up for Claude Fable 5<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b04b9b;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Anthropic 將對 Claude Fable 5 用戶收取額外使用費</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Claude subscribers must soon pay usage-based fees to access Anthropic's best consumer AI model, signaling that the golden era of flat-rate AI subscriptions may be ending.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Claude 訂閱用戶未來須支付額外費用才能使用 Anthropic 最強的消費級 AI 模型，顯示吃到飽 AI 訂閱時代可能即將終結。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">Wired</b> · <a href=\"https://www.wired.com/story/model-behavior-anthropic-will-charge-consumers-extra-to-use-claude-fable-5/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f9edf6;border-left:5px solid #c56bb0;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#c56bb0;font-weight:800;\">10.</span> Humanoid Robots Controlled by Surgeons Did World-First Operation on Live Pigs<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b04b9b;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">研究</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">由外科醫師操控的人形機器人完成全球首例活體豬隻手術</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">A preclinical trial is testing the feasibility of using humanoid robots controlled remotely by surgeons to perform surgical procedures.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">一項臨床前試驗正在測試由外科醫師遠端操控的人形機器人執行手術的可行性。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">Ars Technica</b> · <a href=\"https://arstechnica.com/ai/2026/07/humanoid-robots-controlled-by-surgeons-did-world-first-operation-on-live-pigs/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;font-size:11.5px;color:#9aa1ad;padding-top:10px;\">由 AI News Digest 從各家 RSS 自動挑選、翻譯並寄送</div>\n</div>\n"}